{"tid":1402075,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有攻擊策略，大家係時候推一個散水策略","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:22:12.000Z","uid":140738,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ca4e09608b4de1c56b8bcaadf3b7e8716297fc93","tid":1402075,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:35:33.000Z","msg":"唔好互屌，唔好分化，策略檢討<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n七月以黎被捕人數係咁上升，<br />\n<br />\n愈來愈多人被捕，<br />\n<br />\n証明狗隻已經變左策略，<br />\n<br />\n我地再唔變只會愈拉愈多人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我明有啲義士係做哂心理準備預自己被捕，<br />\n<br />\n但有好多人係無咁嘅心理準備，<br />\n<br />\n純粹見現場仲有好多人留守，<br />\n<br />\n自己唔好意思走先。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以大家應該多啲推崇一個散水概念，<br />\n<br />\n就係自己決定自己走唔走，<br />\n<br />\n唔好因為前線有人留守就唔走，<br />\n<br />\n走唔需要覺得唔好意思。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果因為前線有人唔走而無人走<br />\n<br />\n咁就會形成另一種大台，<br />\n<br />\n無大台，兄弟爬山先係依場運動嘅特色。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nReference, <br />\n雖然係01，純粹比大家睇下數字<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/357974/逃犯條例-50日逾10場大型衝突-最少223人被捕-44人被控暴動\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F357974%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-50%E6%97%A5%E9%80%BE10%E5%A0%B4%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%91223%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-44%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95&d=CmeYdDJU3P8b8ZKgyBn5o%2Fsf6ZhrNwlVLGl95Ukzwcs%3D&h=c16cc5ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/357974/逃犯條例-50日逾10場大型衝突-最少223人被捕-44人被控暴動</a>"},{"pid":"b954ccd98d35eb4a3d0f3db3e2aae372ac1df371","tid":1402075,"uid":9049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:36:20.000Z","msg":"不留守，不被捕"},{"pid":"ee1b4ad50e5384f01e25acf2cc2ee8b8ab56f3b8","tid":1402075,"uid":140738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:37:03.000Z","msg":"85罷工"},{"pid":"ec0466aef824f954de8f3ca348c8985c8160dca8","tid":1402075,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:38:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb0aa